    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 15th level, you wield a steel mind and neigh unbreakable morals. When you succeed a Wisdom saving throw against a jutsu, you suffer no damage or effects.</p><p>Additionally, when you are made to make a saving throw against a jutsu or hostile effect, you can choose to make a Wisdom saving throw instead of the intended save. This can be used a number of times per long rest equal to half your Proficiency Modifier, rounded down.</p>",
